languages.text: {n}Мастер дисциплины мрачно цедит:{/n} "Им помогали. Мы обнаружили спрятанные трупы нескольких служителей часовни. Предатели забрали их одежду и провели Немезита и его подручных мимо патрулей".

{n}Sauerback mutters through clenched teeth,{/n} "They had help. We have discovered the hidden corpses of several chapel attendants. The traitors took their clothes and led Nemesite and his accomplices straight past the patrols."

languages.text: {n}ザウアーバックは歯を食いしばってつぶやいた。{/n}「奴らは助けを借りたのです。隠してあった礼拝堂の従者の死体をいくつか発見しました。裏切り者たちは彼らの服を奪い、ネメサイトと共犯者たちをパトロール隊の前を素通りさせたのでしょう」
languages.original_text: {n}Sauerback mutters through clenched teeth,{/n} "They had help. We have discovered the hidden corpses of several chapel attendants. The traitors took their clothes and led Nemesite and his accomplices straight past the patrols."

languages.text: {n}苏尔贝克咬着牙齿，喃喃说道。{/n}“他们有内应。我们发现了几具礼拜堂侍从的尸体，那些叛徒换上了他们的衣服，带着涅墨斯特和他的同伙直接从巡逻队身边溜过去了。”

languages.text: {n}Sauerback marmonne entre ses dents serrées :{/n} « Ils avaient des complices. Nous avons découvert les cadavres soigneusement dissimulés de plusieurs auxiliaires de la chapelle. Les traîtres leur ont pris leurs vêtements pour échapper aux patrouilles et conduire Némésite et ses comparses à destination. »

languages.text: {n}Sauerback sıktığı dişlerinin arkasından homurdanıyor.{/n} "Yardım almışlar. Birkaç şapel görevlisinin gizlenmiş cesetlerini bulduk. Hainler onların kıyafetini almış ve Nemezit ile eşlikçilerini direkt devriyelerin yanından geçirmişler."
